a.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/110%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c87%2c20211126%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,110,訴,87,20211126,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"87","JDATE":"20211126","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例等"}